data.description: Welcome home where contemporary style meets unmatched convenience. Built in 2022, this 3-bed, 2-bath gem offers a thoughtfully designed living space. Situated on a desirable corner lot, you'll enjoy unparalleled privacy in a community-oriented setting. As you step inside, the open floor plan instantly captivates your attention. The lavish LVP flooring seamlessly connects the main living areas, while plush carpeting adds a cozy touch to all bedrooms. The kitchen is a modern dream, boasting granite countertops and stainless steel appliances that are as functional as they are stylish. The attention to detail extends to the bathrooms, also adorned with granite finishes, setting a tone of understated luxury. Convenience is key; your new home is just minutes away from major highways—close to 74 and mere minutes from I-85. Whether you're looking to venture out or entertain within, this home serves as an ideal foundation for a multitude of lifestyles. Fresh Paint throughout the entire inside
